description:
I should be able to login the axon website
And create a new process

elements.name: Create a new process with mandatory fields

steps.name: I open the site "http://ms-axon-development.local:8888/"
login by giving valid username and password
I should see "John Admin" as the username
I click on "Create", move to "Business & change" and select the "Process" option
I see "New Process" tab, Fill details, Save it
then I get the "Edit" option for the New Process

elements.name: Create a new Process, specifying only the timeperiod for Duration

steps.name: I open the site "http://ms-axon-development.local:8888/"
login by giving valid username and password
I should see "John Admin" as the username
I go to page "http://ms-axon-development.local:8888/process/new"
provide manadatory inputs with Duration as "20"
I get the new process created with "20" in 'Duration'

elements.name: Create a new Process, specifying only the Hours/Days for Duration

steps.name: I open the site "http://ms-axon-development.local:8888/"
login by giving valid username and password
I should see "John Admin" as the username
I go to link "http://ms-axon-development.local:8888/process/new"
provide manadatory inputs, select only Hours/Days as Duration
I get the Process saved with "Not Specified" text in 'Duration'

elements.name: Trying to Create a new Process, without specifying certain mandatory field

steps.name: I open the site "http://ms-axon-development.local:8888/"
login by giving valid username and password
I should see "John Admin" as the username
I visit the page "http://ms-axon-development.local:8888/process/new"
I provide inputs, missing the "Name" field
I get the alert message

elements.name: Verifying Admin User name after login

steps.name: I open the site "http://ms-axon-development.local:8888/"
login by giving valid username and password
I should see "John Admin" as the username
I should see "Welcome to Google"

name: Create a process and validate its view
